Roles and Permissions Structure
1. Admin

Permissions:

create_user

update_user

delete_user

create_institution

update_institution

delete_institution

create_class

update_class

delete_class

create_exam

update_exam

delete_exam

manage_transport

2. Teacher

Permissions:

create_attendance

update_attendance

delete_attendance

view_class_schedule

manage_exams

3. Student

Permissions:

view_own_attendance

view_exam_results

view_class_schedule

4. Parent

Permissions:

view_child_attendance

view_child_exam_results

5. Transport Manager

Permissions:

manage_transport

create_transport_routes

update_transport_routes

delete_transport_routes

assign_transport_to_students

6. Exam Coordinator

Permissions:

create_exam

update_exam

delete_exam

manage_exam_schedule

publish_exam_results

7. Class Coordinator

Permissions:

create_class

update_class

delete_class

assign_teacher_to_class

manage_class_schedule